### Years interviewees have lived in their communities

When we examine the number of years living in the community (@fig-Years_living_in_community_gender), we find that the men interviewed had on average lived in the community longer than the women interviewed. In addition, the results reveal that some people interviewed had moved into the community in recent years.


::: {.cell .fig-cap-location-bottom}

